OL,3,CCrack down in Sussex on the misuse of
OL,4,CBlue Badges
OL,6,FBrighton and Hove City Council and
OL,7,FSussex Police have teamed up to crack
OL,8,Fdown on the misuse of Blue Badges.
OL,10,FOperation Bluebird aims to protect
OL,11,Fdisabled parking spaces for residents
OL,12,Fand visitors who genuinely need them.
OL,14,FIt is estimated that 20% of the 36,000
OL,15,FBlue Badges issued in East Sussex and
OL,16,FBrighton & Hove are misused, according
OL,17,Fto the council.
OL,19,FBlue Badge misuse is a fraud offence
OL,20,Fand is punishable by up to two years
OL,21,Fin prison or an unlimited fine.
