OL,3,CCrack down in Sussex on the misuse of
OL,4,CBlue Badges
OL,6,FBlue Badge fraud includes individuals
OL,7,Fusing someone else's badge to park in
OL,8,Fdesignated disabled bays.
OL,10,FCouncillor Trevor Muten, Cabinet
OL,11,Fmember for Transport, Parking and the
OL,12,FPublic Realm, said: "The misuse of
OL,13,FBlue Badges is not only unfair but has
OL,14,Fa direct impact on the mobility and
OL,15,Findependence of people with
OL,16,Fdisabilities who rely on these spaces.
OL,18,F"Through our collaboration with Sussex
OL,19,FPolice, we are taking decisive action
OL,20,Fto ensure these spaces are used
OL,21,Fappropriately.
