OL,6,F"Misusing a Blue Badge is a serious
OL,7,Foffence, and we will continue to work
OL,8,Fto protect the rights of disabled
OL,9,Fresidents and visitors."
OL,11,FResidents are urged to report any
OL,12,Finstances of Blue Badge misuse.
